<item>
            <title>[LU-9311] mdt_layout_change() shouldn&apos;t reprocess granted resent request</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9311</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the LOVEA buffer is bigger than the request reply buffer, the client will resend the layout write intent RPC, and mdt_layout_change() should not reprocess it since the 2nd process will try to cancel the 1st granted CR lock, while client has not get it granted yet because of the reply buffer shortage resend the RPC.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached are the mds and client log of this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
